Lvl. 35 Beast Mini-boss
15 health
16 attack
20 defense
Veronica, as any siren, was attracted to the sound of troubled men. The dungeon was filled with hundreds of men starving and dying each day. She was hunted until the day the dungeon was abandoned and now feasts on the spoils.
After killing,
Roll 2D6 > 6 for 1 chest items
Roll D6 > 5 for 2 room items
